name validation =>
    (1) number not allowed   (2) mininum length  (3) max length is optional 

number validation => 
    (1) alphabet not allowed (2) special character not allowed (3) mininum length (4) max length complusory 

email validation => 
    (1) @ and dot complusory 

password validation => 
    (1) compare password (2) show password (3) strong password validation (as per required) 

radio button => select complusory 
checkbox validation => select checkbox 
dropdown = select menu 

regular expression => some special characters to match pattern (it is like command symbol) 

events => click, blur(when element lost focus), keyboard event 
